OL,3,CYeovil Hospital's maternity unit to
OL,4,Ctemporarily close, ITV understands
OL,6,FThe maternity unit at Yeovil District
OL,7,FHospital will be closed down
OL,8,Ftemporarily due to a shortage of
OL,9,Fspecialist staff.
OL,11,FStaff members say they were told in an
OL,12,Femergency meeting on Tuesday, 13 May
OL,13,Fand Somerset NHS Foundation Trust has
OL,14,Fconfirmed it will close from 5pm on
OL,15,FMonday.
OL,17,FThe temporary closure comes after
OL,18,Fmaternity services at the hospital
OL,19,Fwere rated inadequate by the Care
OL,20,FQuality Commission (CQC), last year.
