OL,3,CYeovil Hospital's maternity unit to
OL,4,Ctemporarily close, ITV understands
OL,6,FAccording to the CQC's report, there
OL,7,Fwas not enough emergency equipment in
OL,8,Fthe unit to safely care for babies,
OL,9,Fand the service didn't always have
OL,10,Fenough medical staff.
OL,12,FIt also found not all staff followed
OL,13,Finfection control principles, like
OL,14,Fwashing their hands before
OL,15,Fadministering care.
