OL,6,FMaternity services at Taunton's
OL,7,FMusgrove Park were similarly rated
OL,8,Finadequate and bosses of both
OL,9,Fhospitals were sent warning notices of
OL,10,Fthe need to improve. The report found
OL,11,Fstaff had failed to complete mandatory
OL,12,Ftraining, with knowledge gaps
OL,13,Fincluding how to manage when unborn
OL,14,Fbabies had reduced movements or growth
OL,15,Frestrictions.
